WEBVTT

00:06:59.083 --> 00:07:02.843
In your time, scientists thought
humans could replace organs

00:07:02.867 --> 00:07:05.120
and extend life for hundreds of years.

00:07:06.311 --> 00:07:07.657
And they did,

00:07:07.681 --> 00:07:09.683
but eventually, they died anyway.

00:07:11.381 --> 00:07:14.771
In your time, Earth
is the only place people live.

00:07:17.826 --> 00:07:21.211
In my time, Earth is the place
people come to die.

00:07:25.539 --> 00:07:29.059
So when Navid started to show the signs,

00:07:29.083 --> 00:07:31.515
our friends assumed I would do
what everyone does,